<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Tobum Mobotum</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-30 20:47:14</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This weapon has great potentional.<BR>
<BR>
All of us will agree its got a really nice dmg, and a really poor delay.  However, this weapon should be in every tank's arsonnel.  This is what I like to call a group weapon.  If the group has two or more tanks, one should be using this.  Example:<BR>
<BR>
Gaidak, Balagog, and I are hunting in a group in Fronteir Mts.  One of use duel wields, one uses his normal 2h, and the third the Weighted Axe.  We cut him down amazingly fast.  This way the MOB is always taking dmg, both small, med, and extreme.  Gaidak was hitting for 116 often, and double.  A warrior with a crit would topple for mad dmg.  Overall, a nice drop, uncommon, and a good tool.<BR>
It does appear to have a cap until lvl 30 though, as I (28) couldnt hit for over 60, but Gaidak (35) could hit for 116+<BR>
<BR>
...the Troll Has Spoken =P<BR>
<BR>
Tobum Mobotum<BR>
28th Barsher of da Family<BR>
Qu'ellar Elamshinae</font></td></tr></table>
